item.title: How i make my own server
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

Download a source for some servers you need different Java types so watch out. If one java edition does not work try another till you get the right one or look for codes you can place in the compile button it may work even with the wrong java edition but you will not be able to keep the edits you make and after each edit always compile your server and sometimes it will tell you if there is and error so you can change it. The main thing to edit is Client.java. If you wish to edit a characters stats simply open up Characters file choose the file you wish and if its oyu and your want 135 all stats just make your self a admin by typing 3 in player rights then logging in and typing ::master if oyu need any help fell free to add me on msn : junaidasif@hotmail.co.uk
